ver used.","'Input' is defined but never used.","'setIsAdmin' is assigned a value but never used.","'onChangeFile' is assigned a value but never used.","jsx-a11y/anchor-is-valid","The href attribute requires a valid value to be accessible. Provide a valid, navigable address as the href value. If you cannot provide a valid href, but still need the element to resemble a link, use a button and change it with appropriate styles. Learn more: https://github.com/jsx-eslint/eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y/blob/HEAD/docs/rules/anchor-is-valid.md","'useContext' is defined but never used.","'useEffect' is defined but never used.","'Navigate' is defined but never used.","'Field' is defined but never used.","'PhotoIcon' is defined but never used.","'Yup' is defined but never used.","'profile' is assigned a value but never used.","'handleFileChange' is assigned a value but never used.","Invalid alt value for img. Use alt=\"\" for presentational images.","The href attribute is required for an anchor to be keyboard accessible. Provide a valid, navigable address as the href value. If you cannot provide an href, but still need the element to resemble a link, use a button and change it with appropriate styles. Learn more: https://github.com/jsx-eslint/eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y/blob/HEAD/docs/rules/anchor-is-valid.md"]